quran[45]{c,v,t}:
  50,1,"Qaaf, Nditsuba khukurani yoluyali"
  50,2,"Bawukanga mbu Omwikanyilisi yabeetsela okhurula mubo! Abakhayi nibaboola mbu: “ po kano nikokhuchenjia.”"
  50,3,"Mbu nikhulifwa mana khube liloba, okhukalukha okho khuli ehale (shikhunyalikhana tawe)"
  50,4,"Toto khwamanya shosi shiosi shilemukha khusialo mubio, ne khuli nende eshitabo eshibikhanga koosi"
  50,5,"Halali bakhaya obwatoto olwabwabeetsela, mana abo bali mubukoyanu"
  50,6,"Shibalolangakhwo likulu hekulu wabu, shingala khwaliumbakha mana nikhulirona, shililikhwo nolwafwa tawe"
  50,7,"Ne liloba khwalikwaalasia mana nikhuliramwo\ttsingulu,\tmana nikhumesiakhwo buli imbia yemimela"
  50,8,Kho shibe eshilolelo nende eshitsulisio khu buli omusumba ulunjikha khuNyasaye
  50,9,Ne khweshia amaatsi ketsimbabaasi okhurula mwikulu nikhumesilia emikunda nende imele ichesungwa
  50,10,Nende emitende emirambi chilikhwo ebibuli (chiebulana mubunji)
  50,11,"Omukabo khubandu banje, mana nikhulamusia eshialo shiali nishifwile, ne ni endio nilwa Abandu balilamusibwa"
  50,12,Bakhaya imbeli wabu Abandu ba Nuh nende Abandu ba Rasi nende ba Thamud
  50,13,Nende ba Aa’d nende ba Firaun nende Abana babu Lut
  50,14,"Nende abamenyi ba Aikat (bomumasokholio) , nende Abandu ba Tubaa, boosi bakhaya Abarumwa mana kabekanyilisibwa nikabanyoola"
  50,15,"Ne muparanga\tkhwachong’a olwakhwabaloonga olwokhuranjilila ? halali bo bali nobukanakani khukhuloongwa okhuyiakha"
  50,16,"Netoto khwaloonga Omundu ne khwamanya shimubeyibeyinjia mumwoyo kukwe, nafu khuli ahambi khuye okhushila omusi kwo mwikosi we"
  50,17,"Olwa Abamalaika babili balibukanana, owundi niyekhala omukhono omulunji ne owundi omukaata"
  50,18,Shiyakhaboola liosi liosi tawe halali Raqib nende Atid – balihambi naye (bakaandilka)
  50,19,Ne tsisaalila tsiokhurula omwoyo tsiliitsa khubwatoto. Ako niko kawatechelelanga
  50,20,"Ne ulwika lulikhupwa, eyo niyo inyaanga yeyindukho"
  50,21,Ne buli Omundu aliitsa nali nende Omuliindi nende Omuloli
  50,22,"Aboolelwe mbu: “Toto ewe wali wang’ang’alila kano, mana khukhurere habulafu, kho okhulola khukhwo nyanga yino nokhulayi muno"
  50,23,"Ne owashie aliboola mbu: “ wendi ninaye uno amalile okhurechekhwa.”"
  50,24,Musukune mumulilo buli omukhayi omwandakanyu
  50,25,"Owikalilanga amalayi, wabura eshichelo, owuyendinjia (omukanakania)"
  50,26,"Ulia watsokaasia Nyasaye nende abanyaye baandi, mana musukune mushinyasio eshilulu"
  50,27,"Owashe aliboola “ Nyasaye wanje Omulesi, esie shindamukosia tawe halali ye yali mubukori obwa ehale"
  50,28,"Nyasaye aliboola mbu: “ mulasolana imbeli wanje tawe, ndamala okhubarumila amekanyilisio.”"
  50,29,"Liumaho likalukhanibwa imbeli wanje tawe, ne esie shekholelanga Abasumba banje obubii tawe"
  50,30,"Inyanga yakhulireba Jahanam mbu “ Witsuule ?” nayo ilikalusia mbu : “ Abaandi baliwo umete?”"
  50,31,Ne (Janna) mwikulu ilisitibwa hambi khu baria Nyasaye
  50,32,Kano niko kalakwa khuyesiyesi ukalukha khu Nyasaye mana niyelinda
  50,33,"Ulia waria Nyasaye khukefisile, mana niyetsa nende omwoyo omulunjifu"
  50,34,Injilimwo nomulembe ino ni inyanga eyilaliwa tawe
  50,35,Balinyoolamwo shiosishiosi shiabeenya ne khuli nende bishilakhwo
  50,36,"Ne nibenga bakhwasishia imbeli wabu, abali nende amaani okhushila bano! mana nibayiya khushialo muno. koo banyolakhwo abelushila"
  50,37,Toto mu yako khulimwo nende eshitsulisio khu ulia uli nomwoyo nohomba owareka eshirwi naye alolanga
  50,38,"Ne toto khwaloonga likulu nende eshialo nende biosi bilimwo khutsinyanga tsisasaba, ne shikhwanyoola obuchonyi bwosibwosi tawe"
  50,39,Wisumilisie khukababoolanga ne witsomie elira lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi eliuba nilishili okhurula nende nilishili okhukwa
  50,40,Ne omwitsomiekhwo khandi eshilo nende niwakhamala okhumwinamila (okhusujuda)
  50,41,Ne rechelesia inyanga yomulaanji alilanjilia ahambi
  50,42,"Inyangayabaliwulilaoluyokalwomulango kwa toto, eyo niyo inyanga yokhulamusibwa"
  50,43,"Toto efwe nefwe balamusinjia nende bafwisinjia, ne ewefu namulikalukha"
  50,44,"Inyanga yeshialo shiliatikha lwangu lwangu, okhukhung’asibwa okho khuliba okhwangu khifwe"
  50,45,"Efwe khumanyile muno kababoolanga, ne ewe shobarukanga na amani tawe. Ne wikhoonyele Ikuran okhwitsulisia balia abaria inyanga yeyindukho"